{"tid":1669044,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[Twitter戰線] 我哋使唔使叫埋翻牆手足(三毛除外)加入文宣戰線","createTime":"2019-10-22T10:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T17:48:11.000Z","uid":307203,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a1e741d16b9311f6f9a9e3d75b874d770c50e107","tid":1669044,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:24:46.000Z","msg":"話說大家成日話無咩人去入Twitter 國際文宣<br />\n<br />\nbtw,<br />\n1. Twitter 戰線<br />\nTwitter 共識channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=1e073578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 任務bot<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=b41ea978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n【突發】每晚十點 全民Twitter ！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656182</a><br />\n<br />\n2.Reddit 文宣部<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/redditmansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fredditmansyunzou&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=4c48b3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/redditmansyunzou</a><br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線要人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656389</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就諗緊除咗喺香港叫人去Twitter之外，我哋仲有咩方法去擴大文宣人數呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫翻牆手足(自稱反賊)去一齊打文宣戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n畢竟翻牆人數都數以萬計，而佢哋都有一定嘅反共意識，有時可能仲黃過我哋，因為佢哋喺中共統治之下係親身體驗暴政。<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋係唔係要去connect埋佢哋呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔支持"},{"pid":"401f36a2cc9d6784629c9287751a2886fca1a5e6","tid":1669044,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fc21c38be7a4c8526bc8367f796c04c0c27685f","tid":1669044,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"6176c5f5308e83f2584735a319e6bf7039bdae30","tid":1669044,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987e422fa159406d2524f0c390ddcf07b4f3b2f7","tid":1669044,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:46:44.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fc9e4254ae15377d9d288620199bd414ef7d53","tid":1669044,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"同埋如果可以connect到反賊，可能對中共造成更大嘅威脅，佢都唔想畀我哋成功輸出革命㗎嘛"},{"pid":"a392b906b0d0bf3717cf366365211d092cc8048e","tid":1669044,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"文宣效果都可能大啲"},{"pid":"0d366107b94fc6e191e119857300091a203a6851","tid":1669044,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1487229ac2c200cd62f3583f1b69b5160aba3489","tid":1669044,"uid":186216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src